OL,4,COllie Bibby: Hospital apologises to mum
OL,5,Cunable to visit dying son
OL,6, A hospital has apologised and pledged
OL,7, to review visiting restrictions after
OL,8, it prevented parents from seeing their
OL,9, dying son in his final weeks.
OL,11,FOllie Bibby, of South Benfleet, Essex,
OL,12,Fdied of leukaemia at University College
OL,13,FLondon Hospital (UCLH) on 5 May.
OL,15,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fhighlighted the case in the House of
OL,17,FCommons on Wednesday.
OL,19,FMr Bibby's mother Penny said: "All we
OL,20,Fwant from this is for policies to be
OL,21,Freviewed. This has to stop."
